<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10468922>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Adults of Phyllonorycter spp. a, P. phallustenuis sp. n. (Holotype, gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5277); b, P. daehana sp. n. (Holotype, gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5638); c, P. ginnalae (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5633); d, P. jezoniella (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-4037); e, P. lonicerae (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5453); f, P. nigristella (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5655); g, P. ostryae (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5649); h, P. reduncata (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5328). (Scale bars = 2 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10468922/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10468926>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Male genitalia of Phyllonorycter spp. a, P. phallustenuis sp. n. (Holotype, gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5277); b, P. daehana sp. n. (Holotype, gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5638); c, P. ginnalae (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5633); d, P. jezoniella (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-4037); e, P. lonicerae (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5453); f, P. reduncata (gen. slide no. HNUSEL-5328). (Scale bars = 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10468926/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

